snippet.title: We've Got Hostiles.
snippet.description:
English:

This is a teaser trailer that I made for the chapter "We've got hostiles" in the mod Half-Life: Extended. Everything in this trailer is subject to change and nothing is final.

Español:

Este es un teaser trailer que hice para el capítulo "We've got hostiles" en el mod Half-Life: Extended. Todo en este avance está sujeto a cambios y nada es definitivo.

Moddb:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/half-life-extended

Discord:
https://discord.gg/YjMfby3ZzK
